comments: I believe in some cases the prefix denoted the shape and the suffix denoted the colour. In some cases this either didn't match or I struggled to learn and retain the correct portions of the word. I tried to attach the colours and shapes to the portions of the words in my mind. I didn't use a paper and pen. The speed at which the words/images were shown was too fast to comfortably learn and so I felt like I was always catching up!
